  <brief_title>Influence of Treatment for Patent Ductus Arteriosus on Cerebral Oxygenation in Preterm Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Changes of Cerebral Tissue Oxygen Saturation During Treatment of Patent Ductus Arteriosus in Neonates</official_title>
  <sponsors>
